5.3 DUIM-Sheets Module

display?

Generic function

Summary

Returns true if the specified object is a display.

Signature

display? object => display?

Arguments

object
An instance of type <object>.

Values

display?
An instance of type <boolean>.

Library

duim-sheets

Module

duim-sheets

Description

Returns true if object is a display.

See also

<display>, page 243
